des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your devices. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “UWANT HOME” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “UWANT HOME” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon ""Alexa"" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “UWANT Smart” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “UWANT Smart” skill, and you'll be navigated to “UWANT Smart” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the vacuum.”
“Alexa, turn off the vacuum.”
“Alexa, pause vacuum.”
“Alexa, resume vacuum.”
